Spread-Messaging version 0.03
=============================

The Spread::Messaging module aims to make usage of a Spread network relatively
painless. It does not impose any preconceived notion on how logging, error
handling or message processing should be handled. It strives for maximum
flexibility. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Spread.pm
   Spread::Messaging::Content
   Spread::Messaging::Transport
   Spread::Messaging::Exception

